pageProduct.name: Skin Doctors Wrinkle Freeze 15ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Skin Doctors Wrinkle Freeze is an injection free wrinkle reducer to help improve the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles on the forehead, crows feet, bunny nose squint and smile lines.

Skin Doctors™ wrinkle freeze is clinically developed to relax wrinkles and has been tested to target the biochemical mechanism of wrinkle formation. It modulates the over stimulation of facial muscles (smiling, frowning, laughing, talking) to relax the tension around the forehead, furrow brow, crows feet and mouth. This revolutionary anti-ageing peptide helps to simulate the effect of cosmetic injections by relaxing the muscles to reveal younger, firmer and brighter skin.

Size: 15mL

Ingredients

Water (Aqua), Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Bis-PEG/PPG-16/16 PEG/PPG-16/16 Dimethicone, Acetyl Hexapeptide-8, Caprylyl Glycol, Ethylhexyl Stearate, Propylene Glycol, Ceteareth-20, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Carbomer, Triethanolamine, Phenoxyethanol, Imidazolidinyl Urea, Methylparaben, Ethylparaben, Butylparaben, Propylparaben, Fragrance (Parfum), Citronellol, Hexyl Cinnamal, Butylphenyl Methylpropional, Linalool.

Directions

1. Cleanse skin
2. Pat dry and apply Skin Doctors™ wrinkle freeze and gently massage evenly over forehead, temples, between the eyebrows and around the mouth.
3. For best results, use twice daily, morning and night.
4. Follow with Skin Doctors™ treatment products and complete with supermoist™ to keep skin hydrated after treatment.
